{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/gastronomale-komik-kuliner-asyik/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Gastronomale: Komik Asyik Untuk Kenalan Dengan Kuliner","content":"<p>Biasanya ritual memasak identik dengan perempuan. Tentunya karena banyak perempuan yang menjadi ibu rumah tangga dituntut untuk piawai dalam membuat masakan. Tapi, ilmu memasak juga harus dikuasai oleh para lelaki. Krisna, Theo, Abi dan Tian membuktikannya dalam komik Gastronomale.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52727\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52727\" data-attachment-id=\"52727\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/gastronomale-komik-kuliner-asyik/attachment/01-gastronomale/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-gastronomale.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-gastronomale\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-gastronomale-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-gastronomale.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52727\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-gastronomale.jpg\" alt=\"Para karakter Gastronomale. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-gastronomale.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-gastronomale-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52727\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Para karakter Gastronomale. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Empat sekawan Krisna, Theo, Abi dan Tian berasal dari latar belakang berbeda. Krisna bekerja sebagai programmer perusahaan e-commerce, Abi masih kuliah namun sudah disiapkan untuk meneruskan bisnis restoran keluarga, Theo bekerja di mal sebagai desainer grafis, dan Tian berkali-kali ganti pekerjaan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52728\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52728\" data-attachment-id=\"52728\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/gastronomale-komik-kuliner-asyik/attachment/02-gastronomale/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-gastronomale.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-gastronomale\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-gastronomale-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-gastronomale.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52728\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-gastronomale.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-gastronomale.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-gastronomale-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52728\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Keempatnya tinggal dan berkumpul di kontrakan yang sama. Selain itu, mereka juga disatukan oleh satu hal yang sama: makanan! Tinggal jauh dari keluarga menuntut keempatnya untuk mandiri dalam urusan konsumsi, sehingga Krisna dan kawan-kawan pun mendalami berbagai teknik dan ilmu memasak. Lambat laun, kuliner menjadi hal yang mempererat persahabatan mereka, sekaligus jalan untuk melepas penat dari aktivitas sehari-hari yang padat.</p>\n<p>Gastronomale adalah komik karangan Kathrinna Rakhmavika, komikus yang lebih dulu populer lewat serial komik Mera Puti Emas. Dibantu colorist Panda Madu, mereka menciptakan komik kuliner Gastronomale yang tayang di CIAYO Comics! Tahu nggak, kalau nama Gastronomale diambil dari dua kata: gastronomi alias ilmu tata boga/kuliner, dan male (laki-laki) loh.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52729\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52729\" data-attachment-id=\"52729\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/gastronomale-komik-kuliner-asyik/attachment/03-gastronomale/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-gastronomale.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-gastronomale\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-gastronomale-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-gastronomale.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52729\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-gastronomale.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-gastronomale.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-gastronomale-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52729\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Komik Gastronomale bakal mengajak kamu untuk berkenalan dengan berbagai jenis kuliner dari dalam dan luar Indonesia. Jenis-jenis kuliner yang disajikan bukan hanya sekedar makanan berat ataupun full course ala restoran mewah. Lewat Krisna dan kawan-kawan, kamu bakal diajak untuk mendalami berbagai jenis teh hingga kue-kue tradisional asli Indonesia. Ada juga hamburger gaya Jepang, dan masih banyak lagi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52730\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52730\" data-attachment-id=\"52730\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/gastronomale-komik-kuliner-asyik/attachment/04-gastronomale/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-gastronomale.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-gastronomale\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-gastronomale-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-gastronomale.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52730\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-gastronomale.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-gastronomale.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-gastronomale-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52730\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Cara Gastronomale mengenalkan berbagai macam kuliner tidak disajikan dengan cara menggurui, namun juga dibalut dengan cerita slice of life yang sangat relatable dengan kehidupan sehari-hari kita. Bagaimana Gastronomale menyatukan ilmu kuliner dengan kisah hidup yang ringan, membuat komik ini memiliki unsur healing yang mampu menenangkan hati.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga:Â <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kurang-berselera-makan-anime-bertema-kuliner-ini-akan-membangkitkan-selera-makanmu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kurang Berselera Makan? Anime Bertema Kuliner ini akan Membangkitkan Selera Makanmu</a></strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52731\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52731\" data-attachment-id=\"52731\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/gastronomale-komik-kuliner-asyik/attachment/05-gastronomale/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/05-gastronomale.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-gastronomale\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/05-gastronomale-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/05-gastronomale.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52731\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/05-gastronomale.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/05-gastronomale.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/05-gastronomale-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52731\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Hal ini pun didukung berkat kepribadian para karakter utamanya. Ada Krisna yang kalem dan asyik diajak ngobrol, Tian yang jadi bapak dan pelengket buat teman-temannya, serta Abi dan Theo yang upbeat dan ceria. Keempatnya menyajikan kompleksitas yang unik dan mampu mengisi kekurangan masing-masing.</p>\n<p>Hmm, kayaknya sudah nggak sabar menyimak kelanjutan cerita Krisna dan kawan-kawan ya? Langsung cek aja komik Gastronomale di CIAYO Comics, setiap hari Minggu, pukul 16:00 WIB. Cek juga berbagai <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/genre/slice-of-life\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">komik slice of life</a> lain di CIAYO Comics. Dan jangan lupa untuk menyiapkan snack dan makanan kesukaan kamu sebelum baca Gastronomale!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"b05ff412-3893-59df-89d0-4358a35b4ca9"}}}